trans-unit.resname: LEA·183 | Wheel of Fortune | Card Text: Paragraph 1
trans-unit.source: Each player discards their hand, then draws seven cards.
trans-unit.target: 每位牌手弃掉其手牌，然后各抓七张牌。

trans-unit.source: You don't lose the game for having 0 or less life.
trans-unit.target: 你不因总生命为0或更少而输掉这盘游戏。

trans-unit.resname: LEA·6 | Blaze of Glory | Card Text: Paragraph 1
trans-unit.source: Cast this spell only during combat before blockers are declared.
trans-unit.target: 只能于战斗中宣告阻挡者前施放此咒语。

trans-unit.source: Enchanted land has "At the beginning of your upkeep, you may pay {W}{W}. If you do, you gain 1 life."
trans-unit.target: 所结附的地具有「在你的维持开始时，你可以支付{W}{W}。若你如此作，则你获得1点生命。」
所结附的生物具有先攻异能。

trans-unit.resname: LEA·47 | Ancestral Recall | Card Text: Paragraph 1
LEA·53 | Copy Artifact | Card Text: Paragraph 1
trans-unit.source: You may have Copy Artifact enter the battlefield as a copy of any artifact on the battlefield, except it's an enchantment in addition to its other types.
trans-unit.target: 你可以使复制神器当成战场上任意由你操控的神器的复制品来进入战场，但它额外具有结界此类别。

trans-unit.resname: LEA·41 | Veteran Bodyguard | Card Text: Paragraph 1
trans-unit.source: As long as Veteran Bodyguard is untapped, all damage that would be dealt to you by unblocked creatures is dealt to Veteran Bodyguard instead.
trans-unit.target: 只要~未被横置，所有未受阻挡的生物对你造成的伤害都改为对~造成之。

trans-unit.resname: LEA·6 | Blaze of Glory | Card Text: Paragraph 2
trans-unit.source: Target creature defending player controls can block any number of creatures this turn. It blocks each attacking creature this turn if able.
trans-unit.target: 目标由防御牌手操控的生物本回合能阻挡任意数量的生物，且本回合中，对每个攻击生物而言，若前者能阻挡它，则必须阻挡之。

trans-unit.source: If you would gain life, draw that many cards instead.
trans-unit.target: 如果你将获得生命，则改为抓等量的牌。

trans-unit.resname: LEA·103 | Demonic Hordes | Card Text: Paragraph 2
trans-unit.source: At the beginning of your upkeep, unless you pay {B}{B}{B}, tap Demonic Hordes and sacrifice a land of an opponent's choice.
trans-unit.target: 在你的维持开始时，除非你支付{B}{B}{B}，否则横置恶魔大军且牺牲一个由任一对手选择的地。

trans-unit.source: Add an amount of {B} equal to the sacrificed creature's mana value.
trans-unit.target: 加等同于所牺牲生物之法术力值的{B}。
